---
export interface Props {
  lang?: 'en' | 'de';
}
const { lang = 'en' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="problem" id="the-problem">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="problem__eyebrow section-fade">
      {lang === 'de' ? 'Das Problem' : 'The Problem'}
    </p>

    <h2 class="problem__heading section-fade">
      <span class="problem__heading-line1">{lang === 'de' ? 'Was ungehört bleibt,' : 'What goes unheard'}</span>
      <span class="problem__heading-line2">{lang === 'de' ? 'kostet.' : 'costs organisations everything.'}</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="problem__cols">
      <div class="problem__col section-fade" style="--delay: 0ms">
        <div class="problem__col-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M10 2a8 8 0 100 16A8 8 0 0010 2zm0 4v4m0 4h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem__col-title">
          {lang === 'de' ? 'Die Wissenslücke' : 'The knowledge gap'}
        </h3>
        <p class="problem__col-body">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Das Wissen steckt in den Köpfen der Menschen: 80% des operativen Wissens wird nie dokumentiert. 42% von dem, was jeder Mitarbeitende weiß, kann kein Kollege abdecken."
            : "It lives in people's heads. 80% of operational knowledge is never written down. 42% of what each employee knows, no colleague can cover."}
        </p>
        <p class="problem__col-body problem__col-body--callout">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Ob Prozessreibung, strategische Lücken oder Expertise, die mit dem nächsten Wechsel verloren geht - es bleibt unsichtbar, bis jemand fragt."
            : "During a merger, a restructuring, a strategic pivot: that is exactly the knowledge that decides whether it works."}
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="problem__col section-fade" style="--delay: 100ms">
        <div class="problem__col-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M3 10h14M3 5h14M3 15h8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="problem__col-title">
          {lang === 'de' ? 'Warum bestehende Tools scheitern' : 'Why existing tools fail'}
        </h3>
        <p class="problem__col-body">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Was Ihre Mitarbeitenden wirklich denken, hören Sie selten. Meetings produzieren Konsens. Feedback wird abgemildert, bevor es Sie erreicht."
            : "Your tools only hear what they ask. Surveys ask 12 pre-set questions and get 12 pre-set answers. Consultants interview 20 people over 90 days. Town halls compress insight into consensus."}
        </p>
        <p class="problem__col-body problem__col-body--callout">
          {lang === 'de'
            ? "Transformationen scheitern nicht an schlechten Plänen - sie scheitern an dem, was niemand ausgesprochen hat. Fortune-500-Unternehmen verlieren dadurch 31,5 Milliarden Dollar pro Jahr."
            : "None of them surface what they didn't know to ask. That gap is where transformations quietly fail."}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem__cta-wrap section-fade">
      <a href="#request-pilot" class="problem__cta">
        {lang === 'de' ? 'Jetzt lösen' : 'Solve it now'}
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M2.5 7h9M7.5 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding: var(--space-section) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .problem { padding: var(--space-24) 0; }
  }

  .problem__eyebrow {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .problem__heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-xl), 4vw, var(--text-2xl));
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .problem__heading { margin-bottom: var(--space-10); }
  }

  .problem__heading-line1 { color: var(--color-text-primary); }
  .problem__heading-line2 { color: var(--color-text-primary); opacity: 0.3; }

  .problem__cols {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .problem__cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-4); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .problem__cols { margin-bottom: var(--space-8); }
  }

  .problem__col {
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    transition: border-color 0.2s var(--ease-smooth);
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .problem__col { padding: var(--space-6); }
  }

  .problem__col:hover { border-color: var(--color-text-tertiary); }

  .problem__col-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-ui);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .problem__col-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .problem__col-body {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .problem__col-body--callout {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-style: italic;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-text-tertiary);
    padding-left: var(--space-4);
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .problem__cta-wrap { margin-top: var(--space-4); }

  .problem__cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: var(--radius-ui);
    transition: color 0.15s var(--ease-smooth), border-color 0.15s var(--ease-smooth), gap 0.2s var(--ease-spring);
  }

  .problem__cta:hover {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border-color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }
</style>